Package com.service.politic13

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PoliticInfo
    Manage all the politicians that clients can add We get back to client all the informations about the politicians with this class All the information : the age, the politicla party We manage all the politicians in HashMap with a string for the key that is politician name, and for the value the PoliticInfo's instance
    PoliticUser
    The class whith Jax-ws annotations that will be called by the client In this class we manage the client's politician list, all the information that will be retrieved by the client We call for that 2 class : TwitterManage, PoliticInfo We retrieve API Twitter request from the class TwitterManage
    TwitterManage
    Manage the API Twitter requests with the class PoliticUser In this class we get with Twitter API v2 a Twitter's user detail(especially the ID) and a user's recents tweets The bearerToken for the authentification with Twitter's API v2
